name: Gut Says
description: Gut Says ($GUT) is one of the most used phrases in crypto, made famous by Ansem (@blknoiz06) and often used to make predictions about market behavior. $GUT represents the tokenization of each and every trader's Gut, which guides us to make decisions in not just trading, but everyday life. Gut is a character and metaphor for the emotions that guide our trade decisions and ultimately decide our fate.
